sequenceDiagram
    participant Player
    participant Web as Django Web
    participant GM as GM / Admin
    participant Worker as Django Worker
    participant Cardcom
    participant Morning

    Player->>Web: Submit application
    Web-->>Player: Submission confirmation
    Web-->>GM: New application notification

    GM->>Web: Approve application
    GM->>Web: Generate payment link
    Web->>Cardcom: Create Low Profile page
    Cardcom-->>Web: LowProfileId + hosted URL
    Web-->>Player: Payment link email (/pay/<token>)

    Player->>Web: Open /pay/<token>
    Web-->>Player: 302 to Cardcom hosted page
    Player->>Cardcom: Complete payment
    Cardcom-->>Web: Webhook callback
    Web-->>Cardcom: HTTP 200 quickly

    Worker->>Cardcom: GetLpResult(LowProfileId)
    Cardcom-->>Worker: Verified payment result
    Worker->>Web: Mark payment as paid
    Worker->>Morning: Create accounting document
    Morning-->>Worker: Document created
    Worker-->>Player: Morning sends document email
